  <text>
      <body>
         
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_mandloi_1700_batch3_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre"><p>هو</p></div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div1"  xml:id="trans_div1"><p>He [God] is</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
               <persName ref="#hidayatKhan">هدایت خان</persName>
               بنده
               <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالمگیر</persName>
               بادشاه غازی
               <date calendar="#julus">۲۶</date>
            </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div> 
         <div corresp="#orig_div2"  xml:id="trans_div2"><p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#hidayatKhan">Hidayat Khan</persName> servant of <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_badshah">Badshah</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_ghazi">Ghazi</ref> <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">26</date></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>متصدیان مهمات حال و استقبال پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#kampel">کنیل</placeName>
               سرکار
               دار الفتح
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">اجین</placeName>
               <lb/>مضاف بصوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوا</placeName>
               بداند که چون بموجب نشان عنایت عنوان
               <lb/>خدمت چودرائی پرگنه مرقوم از جناب مکرمت و افضال
               <lb/>حسب الضمن از انتقال چورامن چودهری آنجا به
               <persName ref="#nandlal">نندلال</persName>
               پسرش
               <lb/>بشرط دولتخواهی و آبادانکار و حسن سلوک با رعایا
               <lb/>مرحمت گشته باید که خدمت مزبور را بمشار الیه
               <lb/>مقرر دانسته دست تصلی او را در اجرای امور مضافه
               <lb/>این خدمت قوی و مطلق گردانند در این باب تاکید اکید و
               <lb/>قدغن مزید دانند بتاریخ بیست و پنجم شهر شوال سنه
               <date calendar="#julus">۴۴</date>
               <lb/>از جلوس منعمت مانوس سمت تحریر یافت
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div3"  xml:id="trans_div3">  
            <p>
               <lb/>The current and future officials of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil [Kampel]</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref> Abode of Victory <placeName ref="#ujjain">Ujjain</placeName>, 
               <lb/>subordinate to <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName> should know that according to the kindness-bearing <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nishan">nishan</ref> 
               <lb/>the service of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> in the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>, from the gracious and honourable gentleman
               <lb/>in accordance with the details on the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref> [of this document], on the death of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> Churaman, <persName ref="#nandlal">Nandlal</persName>, his son, 
               <lb/>has been kindly appointed to the service of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of that place [<placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil</placeName>] on condition of loyalty and cultivation [of the land] and good behaviour towards the peasants. 
               <lb/>It is necessary that knowing the service assigned to the said person, 
               <lb/>they shall be robust and unconditional [in giving] a comforting hand to him in the execution of the affairs related 
               <lb/>to this service. Know this matter to be settled,
               <lb/>and all prohibitions in place. Written on the twenty-fifth of the month of Shawwal, <date calendar="#julus">44th year</date>  
               <lb/>of the exalted reign, which is glorious. Ended. 
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_mandloi_1700_batch3_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle">
            <p>
               <lb/>مقرر ضمن خدمت چودهرای پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#kampel">کنپیل</placeName>
               سرکار دار الفتح
               <placeName ref="#ujjain">اجین</placeName>
               <lb/>مضاف بصوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوا</placeName>
               بموجب نشان سعادت عنوان
               <lb/>مرقوم بتاریخ ۲۱ بیست و یکم شهر شوال سنه  
               <date calendar="#julus">۴۴</date>
               از جلوس والا
               <lb/>از انتقال چورامن چودهری پرگنه مذکور به
               <persName ref="#nandlal">نندلال</persName>
               پسرش
               <lb/>بشرط دولتخواهی و آبادان کاری مرحمت باشد
            </p>   
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p>
               <lb/>Confirmed by the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref> that the service of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#kampel">Kanpil [Kampel]</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref> Abode of Victory <placeName ref="#ujjain">Ujjain</placeName>,
               <lb/>subordinate to <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName> according to the blessed <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nishan">nishan</ref> 
               <lb/>written on the date of 21 twenty-first of the month of Shawwal of the <date calendar="#julus">44th</date> year of the exalted reign,
               <lb/>on the death of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> Churaman, <persName ref="#nandlal">Nandlal</persName>, his son, 
               <lb/>on condition of loyalty and cultivation [of the land] should be appointed.
            </p>   
         </div>   
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend=" middle right margin"><p>بتاریخ ۲۹ شوال سنه
            <date calendar="#julus">۴۴</date>
            داخل سیاهه حضور است
         </p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5"><p>On the date of 29 of Shawwal of the <date calendar="#julus">44th</date> year, it is entered in the account book of the government.</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="bottom right margin"><p>بتاریخ ۲۹ شوال سنه 
            <date calendar="#julus">۴۴</date>
            نقل بدفتر دیوان رسید
            <lb rend="empty"/>د
         </p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6"><p>On the date of 29 of Shawwal of the <date calendar="#julus">44th</date> year, a copy reached the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_daftar">daftar</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref>.
            <lb rend="empty"/>dal<note>The precise meaning of this single Persian letter 'dal' written below the clerical note is unclear, but it is a common feature of such notes.</note>
         </p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="bottom centre"><p>محل</p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div7" corresp="#orig_div7"><p><gap/></p></div>
        
         <div xml:id="orig_div8" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="left margin"><p>بتاریخ
            ۲۹
            شوال سنه
            <date calendar="#julus">۴۴</date>
            جلوس والا نقل بدفتر
            <gap/>
            <unclear>دیوان</unclear>
            <gap/>
            حاضر شد
            <g ref="#faqat">فقط</g>
            <lb rend="empty"/>م
         </p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div8" corresp="#orig_div8"><p>On the date of 29 of Shawwal of the <date calendar="#julus">44th</date> year of the exalted reign, a copy was prepared for the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_daftar">daftar</ref> <gap/> <unclear><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref></unclear> <gap/>. Nothing further.
            <lb rend="empty"/>mim<note>The precise meaning of this single Persian letter 'mim' written below the clerical note is unclear, but it is a common feature of such notes.</note>
         </p></div>
      </body>
